{"results":[{"aya":"022","id":4436,"locale":"zh","sura":"044","text":"他就祈祷他的主说：这等人，确是犯罪的民众。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"023","id":4437,"locale":"zh","sura":"044","text":"（主说）：你带着我的众仆在夜间出走吧！你们必定要被追赶。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"024","id":4438,"locale":"zh","sura":"044","text":"你让海水保持平静，他们必定是被淹死的军队。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"025","id":4439,"locale":"zh","sura":"044","text":"他们曾抛下若干园圃和泉源，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"026","id":4440,"locale":"zh","sura":"044","text":"庄稼和美宅，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"027","id":4441,"locale":"zh","sura":"044","text":"以及他们所享受的福泽！","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"028","id":4442,"locale":"zh","sura":"044","text":"结局是这样的：我曾使别的民众继承他们，","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":9,"previousPage":"/zh/s044-3.json","nextPage":"/zh/s044-5.json"}}